title: Uprising in Austria
new-page: true
subtitle: In response to police attacks, the Austrian socialists are rising up...
view-if: year = 1934 and (month = 2 or month = 3) and austrian_parliament_seen
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: austrian_civil_war_seen = 1
face-image: img/schutzbund.png
tags: event

= Uprising in Austria

# pre-emptive democratic victory if sdapo strength >= 6
# long civil war if sdapo_strength = 5 or 4 - opportunity for interference/forced peace
# instant defeat if sdapo_strength < 4

The crisis in Austria is continuing. The "Austrofascist" government led by Engelbert Dollfuß continues to rule by emergency decree. It has been persecuting its political opposition, primarily the social democrats of the SDAPÖ.

[? if sdapo_strength < 6: Now, Austria is entering a state of civil war. When the police attempted to seize weapons from the Republikanischer Schutzbund, the Schutzbund responded with force, shooting at the government troops. Fighting has sporadically broken out between Schutzbund and government forces all over Austria. ?]

[? if sdapo_strength >= 6: The government's attempts to suppress the socialist party and the Schutzbund were met with mass protest, supported by the SPD[? if foreign_minister_party = "SPD":  and the German government?]. [? if eu_austria: They are also supported by the recently formed European Union, with economic sanctions targeting the government. ?] ?]

[? if nsdapo_force : Joining in these fights, the Austrian Nazis have risen up under the direction of Hitler, fighting against Austrofascism in the name of German unity, a cause on which they have surprisingly aligned with the SDAPÖ. This "alliance", if it can be called that, is sure to be fleeting. ?]

Eventually...

- @crushed
- @long_war
- @sdapo_victory
- @nsdapo_victory

@crushed
title: The rebellious Schutzbund has been crushed.
on-arrival: austria_defeat = 1
view-if: sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force < 4

The uprising lasted for no more than a few days before it was crushed. The Schutzbund and SDAPÖ were too weak and too divided to stand against the forces of the state. [? if hitler_deported : Hitler, for his participation in agitating against Dollfuß, has been arrested. There is at least one silver lining to the fascist consolidation, perhaps. ?]

@long_war
title: It is a civil war.
view-if: sdapo_strength = 5 or sdapo_strength = 4
on-arrival: austria_civil_war = 1

Neither side is backing down, and the SDAPÖ have formed an alternative government after defeating the government troops in some cities[? if nsdapo_force :, while Hitler's forces have captured a few towns as well, not aligning with either government. ?]. Austria is in a state of civil war.

- @support_sdapo_party
- @support_sdapo_govt
- @force_peace
- @long_war_2

@support_sdapo_party
title: As a party, the SPD will provide the SDAPÖ with support.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 2
on-arrival: resources -= 2; sdapo_strength += 1
go-to: sdapo_victory if sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force >= 6; long_war_2 if sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force < 6

The SPD raises its resources to provide arms and volunteers for the SDAPÖ.

@support_sdapo_govt
title: The Foreign Ministry will support the democratic Austrian forces.
view-if: spd_in_government and foreign_minister_party = "SPD"
on-arrival: sdapo_strength += 1
go-to: sdapo_victory if sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force >= 6; long_war_2 if sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force < 6

We provide diplomatic and some financial and material support to the SDAPÖ forces.

@force_peace
title: Can we bring the sides together for a peace?
view-if: spd_in_government and foreign_minister_party = "SPD" and sdapo_strength = 5
on-arrival: austria_peace = 1; pro_republic += 3; coup_progress -= 1; socialism += 1

achievement: arbeiter_von_wien

The Austrian government obviously sees us as biased, so there is no way they will let us host peace negotiations. However, negotiations begin nonetheless. In Switzerland, with Fascist Italy as the Austrofascists' protector and Germany as the SDAPÖ's, a peace deal is hammered out. The socialists are disarmed and give up all pretense of revolution, while the right-wing paramilitaries are also disarmed. Dictatorship ends, and normal government is restored, with free elections. [? if hitler_deported : The only true loser here is Hitler, who has been arrested by this new government, neither side willing to defend him. ?]

Given the SDAPÖ's starting position, this is treated as a victory. Now begins the long work of reconstruction...

@long_war_2
title: There is nothing we can do.
on-arrival: austrian_long_war = 1; z_relation -= 6; dvp_relation -= 6; coalition_dissent += 1; workers_spd -= 3; new_middle_spd -= 5; rural_spd -= 6; old_middle_spd -= 6; unemployed_spd -= 4

No matter our efforts, the war continues. Too many lives are extinguished. Refugees begin to flow into Germany, and trade suffers. Many are calling our Austrian interference a mistake.


@sdapo_victory
title: The Austrofascists are backing down!
view-if: sdapo_strength+nsdapo_force >= 6
go-to: true_victory if nsdapo_force < sdapo_strength; contested if sdapo_strength <= nsdapo_force

@true_victory
achievement: arbeiter_von_wien
on-arrival: pro_republic += 5; west_relation += 1; east_relation += 1; austria_victory = 1; reichswehr_loyalty += 0.1; coup_progress -= 2; socialism += 2

The result is that the Austrofascists have backed down! Caught in an untenable position domestically and abroad, they have agreed to restore the National Council and resign from government, holding new elections. Now begins the long work of reconstruction. Our countries are likely to be brought closer together as a result.

[? if eu_austria: This is a great success of the new European Union, and its prestige is seen to rise internationally. ?]

@contested

The result is that the Austrofascists have backed down! Caught in an untenable position domestically and abroad, they have agreed to restore the National Council and resign from government, holding new elections. However...

- @nsdapo: The Austrian Nazis are forming their own government!

@nsdapo
subtitle: The civil war continues...
on-arrival: z_relation -= 2; dvp_relation -= 2; workers_spd -= 2; new_middle_spd -= 3; rural_spd -= 3; old_middle_spd -= 4; unemployed_spd -= 2

Rejecting the capitulation and calling on a general uprising of all German nationalists to fight for a national-socialist Austria, Hitler has turned against the SDAPÖ and directed the violence of the SA against it. He is pushing for total power, taking advantage of the power vacuum the civil war created to do so.

- @support_sdapo_party2
- @support_sdapo_govt2
- @long_war_3
- @nsdapo_victory

@support_sdapo_party2
title: As a party, the SPD will provide the SDAPÖ with support.
subtitle: -2 resources
choose-if: resources >= 2
on-arrival: resources -= 2; sdapo_strength += 1
go-to: sdapo_victory if sdapo_strength >= nsdapo_force and sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force > 1.1; long_war_3 if sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force >= 0.9 and sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force <= 1.1; nsdapo_victory if nsdapo_force >= sdapo_strength and sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force < 0.9

The SPD raises its resources to provide arms and volunteers for the SDAPÖ.

@support_sdapo_govt2
title: The Foreign Ministry will support the democratic Austrian forces.
view-if: spd_in_government and foreign_minister_party = "SPD"
on-arrival: sdapo_strength += 1
go-to: sdapo_victory if sdapo_strength >= nsdapo_force; long_war_3 if sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force >= 0.9 and sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force <= 1.1

We provide diplomatic and some financial and material support to the SDAPÖ forces.

@long_war_3
title: There is nothing we can do.
view-if: sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force >= 0.9
on-arrival: austrian_long_war = 2; z_relation -= 6; dvp_relation -= 6; coalition_dissent += 1; workers_spd -= 3; new_middle_spd -= 5; rural_spd -= 6; old_middle_spd -= 6; unemployed_spd -= 4

No matter our efforts, the war continues. Too many lives are extinguished. Refugees begin to flow into Germany, and trade suffers. Many are calling our Austrian interference a mistake.

@nsdapo_victory
title: There is nothing we can do.
view-if: sdapo_strength/nsdapo_force < 0.9
on-arrival: nazi_austria = 1; old_middle_nsdap += 15*(nationalism/100); rural_nsdap += 15*(nationalism/100); new_middle_nsdap += 10*(nationalism/100); workers_nsdap += 5*(nationalism/100); unemployed_nsdap += 5*(nationalism/100); nationalism += 10

No matter our efforts, Hitler is victorious. He has managed to take over Austria as a new base of Nazi power, immediately consolidating power and announcing his intentions to reunify the state with Germany by any means necessary. How this situation will develop remains to be seen. One thing is certain; this new Austria is quite the pariah, with no friends to look to on the world stage, and the former Entente powers, even Italy, refusing to recognize it.